(178, 1, '2020-06-09 06:54:15', '2020-06-09 06:54:15', '<img width=\"354\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/logo3.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/logo3.png 354w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/logo3-300x85.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px\" />											\n			<h1>Welcome\n</h1>		\n		<p>The Best Collection of WordPress Templates. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec suscipit orci ligula, sed laoreet elit finibus et. Maecenas rhoncus, est vitae varius, mauris enim laoreet nulla, non imperdiet justo nibh eu justo.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Learn More\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/q2-2.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/q2-2.png 1200w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/q2-2-300x225.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/q2-2-1024x768.png 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/q2-2-768x576.png 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/q2-2-600x450.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />											\n			<h1>Tabs</h1>		\n										<img width=\"396\" height=\"782\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/today.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/today.png 396w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/today-152x300.png 152w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 396px) 100vw, 396px\" />											\n			<h2>Today tab</h2>		\n		<p>Updated daily, to keep you informed and inspired by the ever-evolving world of apps and games. Its also a great place to find helpful tips and tricks.</p>		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"791\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/games.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"ht